blocks.name: brtp
blocks.content: A condition for a binary relation over an unordered triple. (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 8-Jun-2011.)
blocks.origin:
thm brtp(class c0, class c1, class c2, class c3, class c4, class c5, class c6, class c7) {
  |- wb(wbr(c0, ctp(cop(c1, c2), cop(c3, c4), cop(c5, c6)), c7), w3o(wa(wceq(c0, c1), wceq(c7, c2)), wa(wceq(c0, c3), wceq(c7, c4)), wa(wceq(c0, c5), wceq(c7, c6))))
  -| wcel(c0, universe)
  -| wcel(c7, universe)

  3bitri(wbr(c0, ctp(cop(c1, c2), cop(c3, c4), cop(c5, c6)), c7), w3o(wa(wceq(c0, c1), wceq(c7, c2)), wa(wceq(c0, c3), wceq(c7, c4)), wa(wceq(c0, c5), wceq(c7, c6))), wcel(cop(c0, c7), ctp(cop(c1, c2), cop(c3, c4), cop(c5, c6))), w3o(wceq(cop(c0, c7), cop(c1, c2)), wceq(cop(c0, c7), cop(c3, c4)), wceq(cop(c0, c7), cop(c5, c6))))

  opex(c0, c7)

  opth(c0, c7, c1, c2)

blocks.content: Another distributive law of converse over class composition. (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 3-May-2014.)

thm cnvco1(class c0, class c1) {
  |- wceq(ccnv(ccom(ccnv(c0), c1)), ccom(ccnv(c1), c0))
} = {
  eqrelriiv(hs0, hs1, ccnv(ccom(ccnv(c0), c1)), ccom(ccnv(c1), c0))
  relcnv(ccom(ccnv(c0), c1))
  relco(ccnv(c1), c0)
  3bitr4i(wcel(cop(cv(hs0), cv(hs1)), ccnv(ccom(ccnv(c0), c1))), wcel(cop(cv(hs0), cv(hs1)), ccom(ccnv(c1), c0)), wex(hs2, wa(wbr(cv(hs1), c1, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c0), cv(hs0)))), wex(hs2, wa(wbr(cv(hs0), c0, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c1), cv(hs1)))))
  exbii(hs2, wa(wbr(cv(hs1), c1, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c0), cv(hs0))), wa(wbr(cv(hs0), c0, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c1), cv(hs1))))
  anbi12ci(wbr(cv(hs1), c1, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c0), cv(hs0)), wbr(cv(hs0), c0, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c1), cv(hs1)))
  bicomi(wbr(cv(hs1), c1, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c1), cv(hs1)))
  brcnv(cv(hs2), c1, cv(hs1))
  brcnv(cv(hs2), c0, cv(hs0))
  vex(hs2)
  bitri(wcel(cop(cv(hs0), cv(hs1)), ccnv(ccom(ccnv(c0), c1))), wex(hs2, wa(wbr(cv(hs1), c1, cv(hs2)), wbr(cv(hs2), ccnv(c0), cv(hs0)))), wcel(cop(cv(hs1), cv(hs0)), ccom(ccnv(c0), c1)))
  opelcnv(cv(hs0), cv(hs1), ccom(ccnv(c0), c1))
  opelco(hs2, cv(hs1), cv(hs0), ccnv(c0), c1)
  opelco(hs2, cv(hs0), cv(hs1), ccnv(c1), c0)
  vex(hs0)
  vex(hs1)
  diff.hs0.s(hs1)
  diff.hs0.c(ccnv(ccom(ccnv(c0), c1)))
  diff.hs0.c(ccom(ccnv(c1), c0))
  diff.hs1.c(ccnv(ccom(ccnv(c0), c1)))
  diff.hs1.c(ccom(ccnv(c1), c0))
  diff.hs2.c(cv(hs1))
  diff.hs2.c(cv(hs0))
  diff.hs2.c(ccnv(c0))
  diff.hs2.c(c1)
  diff.hs2.c(ccnv(c1))
  diff.hs2.c(c0)
}
